a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#play-with-dockerplay-with-dockerhttpsgithubcomplay-with-dockerplay-with-docker-github-starshttpsimgshieldsiogithubstarsplay-with-dockerplay-with-dockersvg-languagehttpsimgshieldsiogithublanguagestopplay-with-dockerplay-with-dockersvg-last-taghttpsimgshieldsiogithubvtagplay-with-dockerplay-with-dockersvgsortsemver-last-commithttpsimgshieldsiogithublast-commitplay-with-dockerplay-with-dockersvg&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Play With Docker gives you the experience of having a free Alpine Linux Virtual Machine in the cloud where you can build and run Docker containers and even create clusters with Docker features like Swarm Mode.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
